在各种选举中将俄语采纳为官方语言是诸多主要候选人的竞选承诺（[[列昂尼德·库奇马|列昂尼德·库奇马]]于[[1994年乌克兰总统选举|1994年乌克兰总统选举]]、[[维克多·费奥多罗维奇·亚努科维奇|维克多·费奥多罗维奇·亚努科维奇]]于[[2004年乌克兰总统大选|2004年乌克兰总统大选]]以及[[地区党|地区党]]于[[2012年乌克兰议会选举|2012年乌克兰议会选举]]）。<ref>[http://books.google.nl/books?id=zzbelxtHoBEC&pg=PA149&dq=Viktor+Yanukovych+2004+promised&hl=en&sa=X&ei=shi-UKONNom70QXJ-4HYAw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Viktor%20Yanukovych%202004%20promised&f=false Migration, Refugee Policy, and State Building in Postcommunist Europe] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.nl/books?id=zzbelxtHoBEC&pg=PA149&dq=Viktor+Yanukovych+2004+promised&hl=en&sa=X&ei=shi-UKONNom70QXJ-4HYAw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Viktor%20Yanukovych%202004%20promised&f=false |date=20190611210621 }} by [[Oxana_Shevel|Oxana Shevel]], [[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]], 2011,ISBN 0521764793</ref><ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2012/jul/05/ukraine-war-of-words-russian Ukraine's war of the words] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2012/jul/05/ukraine-war-of-words-russian |date=20130530142354 }}, [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] (5 July 2012)</ref><ref>[http://www.partyofregions.org.ua/en/news/topic/503b6606c4ca42ee400001fe FROM STABILITY TO PROSPERITY Draft Campaign Program of the Party of Regions] {{Wayback|url=http://www.partyofregions.org.ua/en/news/topic/503b6606c4ca42ee400001fe |date=20121224122831 }}, [[Party_of_Regions|Party of Regions]] Official Information Portal (27 August 2012)</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.novostimira.com.ua/news_28570.html |title="Яценюк считает, что если Партия регионов победит, может возникнуть «второй Майдан»", ''Novosti Mira'' (Ukraine) |accessdate=2015-12-02 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103235134/http://www.novostimira.com.ua/news_28570.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年，[[乌克兰的语言政策|乌克兰在语言上的立法]]使俄语成为几个南部和东部地区的“地区语言”。<ref>[http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/yanukovych-signs-language-bill-into-law-311230.html Yanukovych signs language bill into